title: Keep Pressing Forward | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Keep Pressing Forward | Joel Osteen
description:
Too often, we settle for where we are instead of believing God for greater things. But if you're going to become all that He created you to be, you need to learn to keep pressing forward. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
